stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> MessageStarted : message_start
    MessageStarted --> BlockStarted : content_block_start
    BlockStarted --> BlockDelta : content_block_delta
    BlockDelta --> BlockDelta : content_block_delta（累积）
    BlockDelta --> BlockStarted : content_block_stop → 下一个 block
    BlockStarted --> MessageDelta : message_delta（usage 更新）
    MessageDelta --> Done : message_stop
    Done --> [*] : yield AssistantMessage
